ble&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/eugenp/tutorials/tree/master/spring-boot-modules/spring-boot-bootstrap\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(99, 177, 117); text-decoration-line: none;\">over on GitHub</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.334;\">Finally, if you&#39;re looking to get started with Spring Boot, have a look at our&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.baeldung.com/spring-boot-start\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(99, 177, 117); text-decoration-line: none;\">reference intro here</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 data-id=\"conclusion\" style=\"font-size: 29px; margin-top: 2.1em; margin-bottom: 1.3em; line-height: 1.1; font-weight: 700; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; position: relative;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">6. Conclusion</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"bd-anchor\" id=\"conclusion\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; top: -150px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.334;\">In this example we configured a simple and functional Spring MVC project, using Java configuration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.334;\">The implementation of this simple Spring MVC tutorial can be found in&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/eugenp/tutorials/tree/master/spring-mvc-basics\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(99, 177, 117); text-decoration-line: none;\" title=\"Spring MVC Tutorial\">the GitHub project</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-block code-block-11\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 8px 0px; clear: both;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1em; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 1.334;\">When the project runs locally, the&nbsp;<em st