ass=\"marker\"><code console=\"\" lucida=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 1px 5px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, \">git add .</code></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p helvetica=\"\" neue=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, \">step 4: Run command&nbsp;<span class=\"marker\"><code console=\"\" lucida=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 1px 5px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, \">git commit -m YourCommitName</code></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p helvetica=\"\" neue=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, \">Step 5: Run command&nbsp;<span class=\"marker\"><code console=\"\" lucida=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 1px 5px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, \">git remote add YourRepositoryName https://github.com/YourUserName/YourRepositoryName.git </code></span><span helvetica=\"\" neue=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 39, 41); font-family: Arial, \">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p helvetica=\"\" neue=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, \"><span helvetica=\"\" neue=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 39, 41); font-family: Arial, \">Step 6: Run Command&nbsp;</span><span class=\"marker\" helvetica=\"\" neue=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 39, 41); font-family: Arial, \"><code console=\"\" lucida=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 1px 5px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, \">git push origin master</code></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p helvetica=\"\" neue=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, \">Step 7: Run Command&nbsp;<span class=\"marker\"><code console=\"\" lucida=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 1px 5px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, \">git push --set-upstream YourRepositoryName master --force</code></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p helvetica=\"\" neue=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, \">Please note that I am using the latest version of GIT at the time of writing. Also note that I did not specify any particular branch to push the code into so it went to master. In step 6 the GIT will ask you to authorize the command by asking you to enter username and password in a popup window.</p>\r\n\r\n<p helvetica=\"\" neue=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, \">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p helvetica=\"\" neue=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, \">&nbsp;</p>\r\n',1,0,'',1,'														Git Upload Local Repository to remote Repo(Github)												\r\n												');

